tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE patient_health_data (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    heart_rate INT,
    temperature DECIMAL,
    step_count INT,
    activity_type VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE monitoring_data (
    monitoring_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    temperature DECIMAL,
    oxygen_level DECIMAL
);

CREATE TABLE Patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_name VARCHAR(255),
    date_of_birth DATE,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    weight_kg FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE HealthData (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    heart_rate INT,
    steps INT,
    calories_burned INT
);

CREATE TABLE SleepData (
    sleep_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    date DATE,
    hours_slept FLOAT,
    sleep_quality INT
);

CREATE TABLE patients (
    patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    height FLOAT,
    weight FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE heart_rate (
    heart_rate_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    rate INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE steps (
    steps_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    steps_count INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patients(patient_id)
);

CREATE TABLE sleep (
    sleep_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id INT,
    hours_slept FLOAT,
    quality VARCHAR(10),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (patient_id) REFERENCES patients(patient_id)
);
